instructions: Walk straight down the hallway. Turn right at the open doors and go towards the elevators.
Turn left and walk down the hallway passing a glass door,  Stop when you see a tan door on your left and just before the opening to the right.
Turn left and walk between couch and table. Walk towards book shelf. Make right and walk to the left of the pink couch.

Make a 180 degree turn do the door is behind you. Go down the hall, passing the five structures with horizontal black shelves. As soon you get past the last one, you'll see the elevator bank just ahead of you on the right. Wait there.
Walk straight down the hall, passed the desk. Continue straight until you reach the back right corner of the couch and stop there.
Exit the bathroom and walk left down hallway. Turn left towards open white door.
Move forward and turn left, walk down the hallway. Turn right and walk to the open doorway. Stop and wait here.
Walk down hall towards room with spiral staircase. Make a left at pillar and stop before pink couch.
go to your left and walk straight down the hall until you reach the large opening in the wall on the right
Walk down room with lime green wall to left. Make a left towards the three chairs and stop before closed white door.
Move forward and turn right between the chair and the couch. Move to the window, turn left and move towards the book case. Stop and wait here.

Go to the recycling bins. Proceed to the grouping of two tables, one beige stool and one green stool. Turn right and walk toward staircase.  Pass table and chairs on your right. Wait on the landing of the stairs.
walk between the book shelf and wall. Walk straight between the couch and chairs at the table. Turn left at the couch. Then turn towards the chairs and table with the light on the right.
Walk down hall towards room with lime green wall. Make a right and stop in hall with elevators.
walk down hallway past elevators towards open room. stop in next room with couches in it.

turn right and move past the shelving units on the left, veer to the left and move towards the open green double doors, go through the doors and wait next to the shelf that is on the black wall to the right.
Slight left and walk straight past the furniture and three bins towards the wood flooring.  Stop just before the first elevator.
Move forward. Pass near the back of the couch. In the corner of the couch, turn right. Stop at the middle of the couch.
Turn right, move between the elevators.  Stop between the open double doors.
Walk through green doors and down hallway. Make a left between shelves and stop with big window to your left.
Walk past the desk on the left, through the green doors, past the seating area and column.  Stop at the corner back of the pink couch.
Walk past the trashcan and go through the doorway. Turn left and walk down the hallway. Stop at the open doorway with double doors on the left.
walk past kitchen table through green doors. Walk towards exit sign and stop next to elevators.
Walk straight and left at the three colored bins and stop at the white door.
Turn right go down hallway turn first right and then an immediate right and go into the men's' bathroom and wait.
Turn right, move through the open open double doors.  Turn right, move to the end of the hall. Turn right, wait in front of the drinking fountain.
Walk around the back of the large couch. Turn left towards the open green doorway. Walk through the green doors and stop.
Turn to the left and walk straight from the bank of elevators to the glass doors up ahead.
Walk down hallway to doorway. Walk forward between chair and stools and turn right. Go forward to open doorway and wait.
Make a left down the hallway and veer left towards the elevators, but stop just as you reach the white door.

Walk all the way through room with whiteboard and long counter. Enter the living room. Turn left, walk through the space between the chair grouping and the stools. Walk through the doorway and wait beside the first elevator.
Walk through the teal doors and turn left. Stop next to the white and teal cushions.
Walk past the elevators towards the glass doors.  Stop when you step from the wood floor onto the cement floor.
Walk away from the glass door and turn left after the first doorway. Walk into the doorway with the wooden floors and then stop.

Go through the aqua archway into the hallway with the block carpet. When you get to the first set of diagram paintings on the wall turn into the room opposite it. Go towards the blue and white ottomans on the side of the window.
Turn left, move forward past the back of the couch, turn right at the end of the couch, stop here.
Turn left, move between the stairs and the sectional couch. Turn left, move towards the window. Stop near the window, between two ottomans.
Walk through open white doors. Make a right and walk down hallway towards bathroom. Make a right and stop outside restroom.
Move away from the closed wooden door, move past the elevators on the right.  Stop where there is a black box recessed into the wall.
Turn left, go straight down the corridor. Pass the glass doors on the left. Keep going and wait when you get to the doorway on the right , just before the door on your left.
Move through the open doorway, turn right and move down the hallway. Stop at the water fountain on the right
Walk down hall with lime green wall to your left.  make a right before exit sign and stop with pictures on wall to your left and shelves to your right.
Turn right, leave the bathroom.  Turn left, move down the hallway, stop at the open double doors near the elevators.
Walk between the table and the whiteboard and then turn right and walk down the hallway to your left. Stop after you pass the teal doors and are in the next room.
Walk away from the door and turn right after you pass the white and teal cushions on your right. Turn left once you pass the two white fabric chairs and stop near the peach colored couch.
Walk into room with couches. Make a right towards spiral staircase. make a left and walk towards pink couch on right.
Walk towards the white L-shaped couch and pass it on your right. Turn right and stop once you pass the couch.
Walk forward over the carpet. Stop at the last geometric picture before the elevator hall.
Turn so that the windows are on your right and walk past the large  cement column.  Walk between the shelves with the red books and blue books and then stop.
Go straight until you get to the trash bins. Go to your left until you are just one foot past the blue recycling bin.
Turn left and walk down hallway and stop before restrooms on your right.

Slight right, walk past the elevator and into a room with bookshelves.  Walk past the upholstered chair on the left and turn left and pass a shorter shelving unit and stop at the corner of the pink couch.
Face the room with the spiral staircase and walk forward, stopping once you are standing on the carpet.
walk down hall past glass doors on left. turn right at end of hall outside of bathrooms.
Walk straight towards the exit, but stop and make a right when you see the wall with art and stop.
Make a 180 degree turn and continue straight until you are at the column near the glass door.
Walk past the elevators into the room with carpet, past the three cushions on the right and exit through the green doors and stop when you hit the cement hallway.
Proceed straight past the lounge chairs and make a right at the first book shelf.
Turn left, go down hallway and stop before room with lime green wall in front of you.
Proceed past the elevators and stop when you enter the carpeted room.
Walk forward toward the open green doorway. Stop right as you enter through the green doors.
Move straight until you are between the third and fourth set of bookshelves.
Walk down hall and make a right before chairs. Walk towards pillar and stop before spiral staircase.
Walk down hallway. Make a right and stop in between open white doors.
Walk towards the glass wall and turn right.Continue down the hall and turn right at the first doorway. Turn right and enter the men's bathroom and then stop.
walk forward down the hallway, past the elevators, stop before the glass doors in front of you
Advance to the end of the hall. Turn left. Stop after 5 feet.
Move forward past the elevators, stop at the doorway under the exit sign
Make a right in front of the couch, veer straight, then right to proceed past the windows and stop between the first two bookshelves in front of the first hanging piece of art.
Walk between bookshelves on the right to enter the hallway. Walk down the hallway toward the green wall.
Walk towards the women's restroom and turn left. Turn left again and continue down the hall. Take a left at the hall with the elevators and stop.
Turn left and go between the two bookshelves and make a left at the hall with the artwork.  Make a right and step onto the wood floor and stop.
Turn around and walk down the hallway. Turn right at the open door.
Walk towards bookshelf. Turn left at wall and walk down hallway with pictures on the left. Turn right towards the elevators and stop.
Walk down hall past elevators. Walk through white doors and stop in hallway.
Walk past the elevators and stop at the glass doors.
Walk straight past the elevators.  Turn left after you pass elevators. Stop after first divider to your right.
Walk past elevators toward open doors and stop in the hallway before closed glass doors.
Walk straight past the elevators. Walk past the three circular chairs. Turn right through the open green doors.
Walk past the last bookshelf, veer left and exit through the green door on the right and take one step beyond the door and stop.
Turn left and walk past the back of the couch, make a right and stop at the end of the couch.
Turn right to exit restroom, make a left and walk down until you see glass doors on the right,  Make a small left and stop when you step onto the wood floor before you are in front of the elevator.
Walk to the table, make a right behind the couch, left after the couch and exit through the green doors and stop,
Walk down hall and through green doors. Make a left and walk towards exit sign. Make a right before sign and stop.
Walk in between couch and chair. Turn right and walk in between couch and table. Turn left and walk between pillar and chair. Walk through doorway and stop in next room.
Walk straight past the elevators and stop after stepping through the white doors at the intersection.

turn left and go around the long table, turn to the left and go out the door, make another left and move towards the open green double doors, go through the doors and wait once inside on the carpet where the dining table and chairs are on the right
Walk down the hall with the brown shelving units on your left. Turn right into the hallway with the elevators and then stop.
Turn right, move past the three recycle bins.  Turn right, move to the stairs and wait.
Turn right 90 degrees and walk down the hall. Stop in the hallway right before the bathrooms.
Turn left, move between the red and blue book case, turn left.  Walk down the hall until a right turn is possible.  Turn right.  Stop near the elevators.
Turn left, move down the hall to the restroom.  Stop just inside the men's restroom.
Go between the table bookcase and the sectional sofa on this floor.
Make a right and head towards the staircase and stop at the landing..
Walk past table on your right. Make a left and walk through green doors and stop in next room.
Go to the entrance of the elevator lobby next to the fire extinguisher.
Walk towards the white doors that lead to an area with a gray floor. When you pass the doors turn right. Turn right at the first doorway and then stop.
Go between the first set of bookshelves. Turn left and go straight until you are at the end of the hallway.
Walk straight past the shelving unit an make a left down the hall lined with art and stop just past the last hanging picture,
Go down the hallway towards the bathrooms. Stop right in front of the water fountains
Go to your right, walk down the hallway and to the huge pillar in front of you. Take a few steps to your left until you are aligned with the furthest pillar.
Make a left behind the table and another left towards the green door.  Stop when you enter through the green threshold.
Walk past the elevators and stop just before you step unto the cement flooring.
Walk down hallway past elevators. Turn left out of doors. Stop in room with pictures on the wall to the left.
Turn around and head past the first shelving unit, stop and make a left.  Stop when you reach the blue and white cushions on the right and windows on the left.
Walk towards lime green wall. Make a left and walk through green doors and stop in next room.
Make a turn left and walk past the tan and white wall and through the green door.  Make a left and head past the exit sign and stop.
Walk down hallway between elevators. Walk through white doors and stop before closed glass doors.
Walk into the room with the spiral staircase and turn right into the room past the large monitor on the wall. Stop once you get past the doors.
Walk behind the couch make a left at the end and walk towards the windows and stop.
Walk down the hall with the elevators and then stop once you are no longer on the wooden flooring.
Turn left and face the open walkway with elevators. Walk straight until you reach the elevators.
Move between the elevators and stop between the open double doors.
Walk through hallway past elevators. Walk towards room with green doors and walk through them.
Turn left walk down hall towards exit sign. Stop when in between elevators.
Go down the hallway and through the green door. Then go left towards the exit sign but turn right before the doorway and wait behind the bookcase.
Walk towards big pink couch with pillow . Make right and walk towards big window. Walk in between shelves and stop before wall with pictures on it.
Walk straight past the glass door and make a right when you see a slatted tan door.  Stop outside the women's room sign and drinking fountain.
Walk away from the teal doors and then stop when you reach the first doorway on the right.
Walk straight and exit the room.  Stop when you step onto the wood floor.
Walk in between book shelves. Make a left at wall and walk down hallway and stop in room with lime green wall.

turn to the left and move forward past the elevators on both sides, go through the white open double doors and stop in the middle of the hallway between the white double doors and the glass doors in front of you.
Turn around and past the three partitions. Stop after the third partition
Turn right, walk past the glass doors on the left and continue until you can see a tan door and drinking fountains to the right.
Turn towards the room with the spiral staircase and go forward until you pass two fabric chairs. Then turn left and stop next to the table that has a bookshelf under it.
Walk down hallway. Pass open doors on right. Stop before the restrooms on your right.
Go forward between the couch and the chair then turn right. When you reach a bookshelf turn left. Go forward and past the teal doors and then stop.
Go straight into the hallway. in front of the last group of paintings.
Walk past table on right. Walk towards pillar and make a left. Walk towards big window with the city skyline and stop.
Walk into the room with colored carpet and stop in front of the fourth bookshelf.
Walk down hallway with pictures on wall to the right. Stop before room with lime green wall in front.
Walk intho hallway. Make a left at closed brown door. Walk down hall and make a left and stop by open white doors.
Walk in between table and wall through the green doors. In next room walk towards wooden wall and stop with pink couch to your right.
Face the glass wall and walk to the end of the hall with the wooden flooring and then stop.
Drive straight ahead.
Go to the end of the hall and take a right to get to the elevators.

Continue forward until approximately four feet from the door at the end of the hallway. Turn to about a 60 degree angle and continue straight towards the closed door. Once arrived, kindly enter through the opened door on the left.
Turn left and walk down hallway. Turn right towards restrooms. Walk through mens room door and stop.
Turn around and walk to the right towards the couch in front of the windows.  Stop when you reach the corner back of the couch.
Walk away from the spiral staircase and towards the hall with the elevators. Stop when you are about halfway through the hallway.
Walk down hall. Stop with glass doors on left and open doors on right.
Walk away from the glass door and stop at the last shelving unit on your left.
Head straight through the green doors, make a left past the three small chairs, right into the hall with the wall art.  Stop at the first piece of art.
Walk in between green doors. Walk down hallway. Stop in middle of hallway with shelves to the left and pictures on wall to the right.
Head down the hallway away from the stairs. Turn right at the white doors with the wooden flooring and then stop.
Continue forward with the whiteboards on your left. Keep walking and you will be in a new room. Stop before you reach the peach-colored couch on your right.
Walk behind the couch and stop in front of the lower shelving unit.

Face down the hall so that the glass door is on your left side and go forward. Turn right before you reach the door at the end of the hallway and you should see some water fountains. Turn right and walk into the men's restroom and then stop.
Turn right and proceed to the end of the hallway, turn right to see a drinking fountain, and another rand enter the Men's restroom. and stop.
turn to the right and move down the long hallway passing the open white double doors on the right , stop and wait when you pass the glass doors on the left.
Walk down hall past elevators. Stop in between open white doors.
Walk towards big pink couch. Make a right at couch and walk between table and couch and stop before bookshelf.
Go next to the three garbage cans in the carpeted room.
Walk forward between the teal doors and keep going. Stop about halfway down the hall with the dark brown wooden shelves on the left.
Turn right and walk down hallway. Turn right before the closed doors and go into mens restroom.
Follow the arrow that says 'conference center' but continue straight down the hall in that direction. Stop in front og the wooden door.
Head past the elevators and make a left after entering the room and stop at the first wall art hanging on the left.
Move away from the stairway, towards the three recycling bins. Turn left at the bins and stop at the door.
Turn right, move past the three recycle bins.  Turn right and move towards a very large column. At the column, turn left and stop between the purple books and the couch.
Go straight until you get to the bookshelves. Go 2 feet past the bookshelves, then turn to your right.
